# Gopher Code — Demo Recording
# Run: ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=... vhs scripts/demo.tape

Output assets/demo.gif
Set Width 1400
Set Height 800
Set FontSize 20
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set CursorBlink false

Type "gopher-code"
Enter
Sleep 8s

Type "read the README and tell me what this project is"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 25s

Ctrl+C
Sleep 2s
